sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.win32.coff

Interface OptionalHeaderDataDirectories


  • public interface OptionalHeaderDataDirectories
    Models the information stored in the data directories portion of the optional header of a Portable Executable file. FIXME: the DataDirectory objects are less than useful; need to bring up more of the data structures defined in the documentation. (Some of the descriptions are taken directly from Microsoft's documentation and are copyrighted by Microsoft.)
